- src/Particle/ParticleBase.h : ParticleBase — Base class for managing and storing particle data in the IPPL scientific C++ codebase.
- src/Particle/ParticleAttrib.h : ParticleAttrib — Templated class for all particle attribute classes, used to represent a single particle attribute.
- src/Particle/ParticleBase.hpp : create, createWithID — Methods for creating particles with or without IDs and globally.
- src/Particle/ParticleBase.hpp : addAttribute — Adds attributes to particles.
- src/Particle/ParticleAttribBase.h : ParticleAttribBase — Base class for all particle attribute classes.
